
= srr : simple realsense (RGB) recorder =

date : 2020-09-24
version : 0.1 , very minimal features

for single device (d435)
    camera stream -> .bag (will be deleted) -> png images -> .avi (mpeg)

Dependency
- bash
- librealsense
- ffmpeg

Install [defalut path : ~/.local/bin/]
- sh install.sh

Uninstall
- sh uninstall.sh

Quick Strat
- srr <recording time: default=30s> <dirname: default=current time>

Examples
- srr
- srr 10 abc

